title: Activation - Futuristic UI & HUD Sound Effect Library
description: The ACTIVATION Sound Library features more than 1,100 sounds. The futuristic and electronic sound effects are especially useful when it comes to creating user interfaces (UIs) and  head-up displays (HUDs).
longDescription:
The ACTIVATION Sound Library features more than 1,100 sounds. The futuristic and electronic sound effects are especially useful when it comes to creating user interfaces (UIs) and head-up displays (HUDs).

The ACTIVATION Sound Library offers 12 categories, granting easy access to a variety of sounds — alerts, beeps, bells, buttons, clicks, counter sounds and many more.


Demo: https://soundcloud.com/user-147860445/sets/activation-ui-hud-sound-effects-library


The sounds provided by the ACTIVATION Sound Library have been carefully produced, selected, edited and tested.

The ACTIVATION Sound Library offers a great variety. The sounds are based on analog and digital synthesizers, guitar effects units, professional software as well as a modular synthesizer rack.
